  ('optometrist-moex-03015', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-107-28e89c47', 'sub-optometrist-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關漸進多焦點鏡片的鏡框選擇，下列何者不是考慮之重點？', '["選擇較小頂點距離的鏡框", "適當的前傾角（pantoscopic tilt）", "鏡框的鼻側要有足夠的垂直深度", "鏡框的顳側要有足夠的水平寬度"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f85cd30c1fda", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2c2bddf06560", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "112", "s": "1104", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學與配鏡學", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03016', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-107-28e89c47', 'sub-optometrist-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '鏡框尺寸A=50 mm、B=30 mm、DBL=18 mm、PD=62 mm、無框的ED=70 mm，下列敘述何者正確？〔A： 鏡框水平長度（horizontal boxing length）；B：鏡框垂直長度（vertical boxing length）；DBL：鼻距（distance between lens）；PD：瞳距（pupil distance）；ED：有效直徑（effective diameter）〕', '["鏡框的中心距DBC（distance between centers）為48 mm", "右眼鏡片的光學中心（optical center）在鏡框的幾何中心（geometrical center）的內側6 mm", "最小鏡坯的直徑選擇為70 mm", "鏡框差（frame difference）為32 mm"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f85cd30c1fda", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2c2bddf06560", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "112", "s": "1104", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學與配鏡學", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": true, "flags": ["answer_corrected_skip_v1"], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03017', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-107-28e89c47', 'sub-optometrist-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '偏光眼鏡鏡片具有方向性，可降低來自水平表面的反射光強度，而達到消除眩光的功能，此現象是因為 入射光在某一角度（布魯斯特角 Brewster''s angle）會全部被偏振，則此偏振光（polarized light） 的方向 為何？', '["垂直方向", "水平方向", "45 度方向", "135 度方向"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f85cd30c1fda", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2c2bddf06560", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "112", "s": "1104", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學與配鏡學", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 40, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03018', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-107-28e89c47', 'sub-optometrist-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關球面透鏡的視覺像移（image displacement），下列何者錯誤？', '["正球面透鏡的視覺像移與鏡片移動方向相反，稱之為逆動", "配戴負球面透鏡看物體時，因像比實物小，故感覺較實際距離遠", "鏡片的幾何中心是兩條不會產生視覺像移且互相垂直的線之交點", "將兩個屈光度相同但正負符號相反的球面透鏡重疊，則不會產生視覺像移"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f85cd30c1fda", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2c2bddf06560", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "107110", "c": "112", "s": "1104", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "隱形眼鏡學與配鏡學", "year": "107", "exam_name": "107年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、107年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 41, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
